---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Heartwood Wellbeing">
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-600 via-yellow-600 to-orange-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-amber-100">Terms and conditions for our holistic therapy services</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms of Service Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-6">Terms and Conditions</h2>
          
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            These terms and conditions govern your use of Heartwood Wellbeing's services and website. 
            By using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">1. About Our Services</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Heartwood Wellbeing provides holistic therapy services including massage therapy, sound healing, 
            aromatherapy, and companion care for seniors. Our services are provided by Kelly, a trained 
            Holistic Therapist, and are designed to promote wellbeing and relaxation.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">2. Booking and Appointments</h3>
          <ul class="text-amber-800 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Appointments can be booked via WhatsApp, phone, or email</li>
            <li>We require 24 hours notice for cancellations</li>
            <li>Late cancellations (less than 24 hours) may incur a 50% charge</li>
            <li>No-shows will be charged the full session fee</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to refuse service if we believe it's not appropriate</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">3. Health and Safety</h3>
          <ul class="text-amber-800 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Clients must disclose any medical conditions, allergies, or contraindications</li>
            <li>Our services are complementary and do not replace medical treatment</li>
            <li>Clients should consult their GP before starting any new therapy</li>
            <li>We maintain professional indemnity insurance</li>
            <li>All equipment and products used are safe and appropriate</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h3>
          <ul class="text-amber-800 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Payment is due at the time of service unless otherwise agreed</li>
            <li>We accept cash, bank transfer, and other agreed payment methods</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change with 30 days notice</li>
            <li>Refunds are at our discretion and subject to individual circumstances</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">5. Confidentiality</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            All client information is treated as strictly confidential. We will not share your personal 
            information with third parties without your explicit consent, except where required by law 
            or for your safety.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            While we take every care to provide safe and effective services, we cannot guarantee specific 
            outcomes. Our liability is limited to the cost of the service provided. We are not liable 
            for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">7. Website Use</h3>
          <ul class="text-amber-800 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>This website is for informational purposes only</li>
            <li>Content is provided "as is" without warranties</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the website</li>
            <li>Users must not misuse the website or its content</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">8. Complaints and Feedback</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We welcome feedback and take complaints seriously. If you have any concerns about our services, 
            please contact us directly. We will investigate and respond to all complaints within 7 days.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">9. Changes to Terms</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page and will 
            take effect immediately. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-4">10. Contact Information</h3>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-amber-800 mb-4">For questions about these terms or our services:</p>
            <p class="text-amber-800 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@heartwoodwellbeing.co.uk" class="underline hover:text-amber-600">info@heartwoodwellbeing.co.uk</a></p>
            <p class="text-amber-800 mb-2"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+447931220197" class="underline hover:text-amber-600">+44 7931 220197</a></p>
            <p class="text-amber-800"><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/447931220197" class="underline hover:text-amber-600">Contact Kelly on WhatsApp</a></p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 mt-8">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2025<br>
            These terms are governed by English law and any disputes will be subject to the jurisdiction of English courts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
